reviewText: Did not open package. The disclaimer  on the back of the video said it all.  THIS VIDEO IS NOT SANCTIONED  BY THE ARTIST.  Cloud line media profited from this  sale and so did amazon. ONE REPUBLIC got nothing for it. They did all the  work. Don't  purchase this.
it is a dvd of interviews,  i enjoyed the dvd very much...  it is very interesting to see and hear what has to happen out on the road to sell the music.  it looks like fun and very exhausting...

OMG no music, the cover gives you an impression that it is a live show on DVD, nope it is just interviews which you can find plenty of that on youtube. Save your money if you are wanting live music. Buy it if you are a die hard fan just wanting everything they are on. This isn't put out by the band either.
It's only Interviews... Lol don't buy it if you want to hear them.
